$ ORA-01934: circular role grant detected

code {
create role rol_x;
create role rol_y;
code }

OK:
code {
grant rol_x to rol_y;
code }

The following statement causes *ORA-01934: circular role grant detected*.
code {
grant rol_y to rol_x;
code }

